programme.title: Old Bay and Old Spice Don't Mix
programme.desc: Things get contemptuous as our panel argues over a dish in the 60s...who is right? Who is wrong? Who knows, but we all win!

programme.title: A Favorite of Youngins and Felons Alike
programme.desc: You may not agree with some meals on this episode... but that's okay, because the panel agrees with you!

programme.title: Baja Breaking all the Rules
programme.desc: We're halfway through our list, but somehow just getting started!

programme.title: Eminem's Mom gets a Mention
programme.desc: Our panel continues to disagree with each other in this episode... which makes for good TV!

programme.title: Worthy of the Meat Sweats
programme.desc: You will be surprised by at least ONE of the meals in this episode. Which will it be?

programme.title: Mozarella Ice Cream or Strawberry Pizza
programme.desc: Coming down to the wire, what meals are going to make the cut?

programme.title: The Final Countdown
programme.desc: Can you believe it? The final ten meals are here! Is your favorite on the list?!

programme.title: The Wonderful World of Pizza
programme.desc: Frankie makes pizza magic with two incredible doughs, turning his kitchen into a pizza party with grilled sausage pizza, cheesy Grandma Pies, golden Panzerotti, and a sweet dessert pizza topped with ricotta, berries, and honey.

programme.title: Italian Smokehouse
programme.desc: Frankie fires up a steakhouse-style spread with Italian flair from golden beets and buttery mushrooms to a sizzling Bistecca alla Fiorentina steak with salmoriglio sauce, and a smooth cold brew affogato granita.

programme.title: Lunch That Goes the Distance
programme.desc: Frankie fuels up for action making hot Oatmeal, and Energy Date Balls, before he cooks up the perfect post-ride feast of cheesy Juicy Lucy Burgers, Ramp-loaded pasta salad, and a maple ginger switchel to cool it all down.

programme.title: Pasta From Scratch
programme.desc: Frankie explores his Italian roots, pairing each pasta shape with its perfect sauce—from Cavatelli with Super Green Sauce to Pappardelle in pork ragout, ricotta Gnocchi with punchy anchovy pecorino, and cozy Squash Orzotto with bloomed poppy seeds.

programme.title: Getting the Band Back Together
programme.desc: Frankie reunites his old band for a jam session and a spin on a college-era classic — featuring Shoyu Ramen with Tare Eggs, sweet and savory Chicken Meatballs, Seaweed Cucumber Salad, and a crispy Okonomiyaki pancake.

programme.title: Pancake Stacks and Snacks for Two
programme.desc: Frankie flips the script for his wife Heather making breakfast for dinner featuring Banana Maple Pancakes, Eggs Benedict with prosciutto cotto, Home Fries with Bloody Mary Ketchup, Sausage Scrapple, and a boozy Espresso Milkshake.

programme.title: Beer Brats & BBQ Ribs
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde grills up summer favorites perfect for any backyard BBQ. Cheddar beer brats in a pretzel bun, BBQ lamb ribs with Chinese mustard sauce, watermelon lime soju punch, & warm donuts with grilled strawberries & whipped cream for dessert.

programme.title: Bougie Badass Burgers
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde brings your basic burgers to a new level with his dry-aged beef burger with potatoes and truffle dijon mayo, a part-beef part-pork belly burger with cheddar & an egg, and lastly a crispy mushroom tortilla burger with salsa & cheese.

programme.title: Feast of Killer Crab & Perfect Pork Belly
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde prepares a finger food feast with char grilled chili crab, spiced adobo potatoes, grilled pork belly, & sofrito stuffed branzino all served on a bed of rice over banana leaves. Call your friends - this is a feast that will feed many!

programme.title: Luxe Lobster & Prime Rib
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde pulls out all the stops for this daddy-sized dinner. He grills up prime rib with herb & horseradish crust, lobster & chili sauce American, charred green beans with garlic tahini, and cheddar-stuffed parker house rolls.

programme.title: Summer Seafood Smorgasbord
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde gets his beach vibes going with a grilled shrimp & lobster cocktail, clams with lemon breadcrumbs, a killer grilled king crab with burnt citrus butter, and a chilled mango frozen daiquiri. Don’t you dare miss this beach party!

programme.title: Deluxe Dogs with Crusted Corn & Potatoes
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde puts a modern spin on a classic All-American cookout with his loaded hot dogs, spiced smashed potato salad, chorizo & corn nut crusted corn, and bangin’ banana pudding pops. Sparklers out for this spread!

programme.title: Top of the Line Steaks
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde is back to level up his steak game by grilling up a NY strip steak with roasted onions & poblanos, short ribs with chili paste and horseradish, and a grilled chateaubriand with charred broccolini. Steak your claim on these dishes!

programme.title: Grilled Chicken 3 Ways
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde amps up your chicken dishes by making smoky chicken wings, a whole roasted turmeric ginger chicken with tamarind sauce, and chicken patties grilled in banana leaves with chili lime noodles. A frosty lime rickey finishes it all off!

programme.title: Scrumptious Summer Sandwiches
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde channels his inner sandwich lover by making an angry lobster club with pepper aioli and grilled bacon, a lamb birria torta with avocado and ramen consomme, and his an Italian beef combo with chili crisp cheese sauce, and giardiniera.

programme.title: A Festive & Flavorful Christmas in July
programme.desc: Chef Dale Talde dons his Santa hat & holiday garb while grilling up smoked ham & pineapple praline sliders, sweet potatoes with soy maple bacon, eggplant with labneh & cranberries, a holiday mezze plate, and a grilled coquito cocktail.

programme.title: Zoo Vet At Large
programme.desc: Dr. Matt gets up close and personal with Albert, Flamingoland's 12-foot alligator, as he moves to a new home. Teddy the pet sheep has suspected calcium deficiency and needs emergency treatment, and Marcel the marmoset leads Matt a merry dance around the surgery. Back at Flamingoland, a reluctant macaw needs his beak trimming -V and Matt comes face-to-face with the new pride of lions.

programme.title: ...Make You Laugh Out Loud
programme.desc: We've scoured the internet to bring you the most hilarious clips of Budgies (and other birds) on the planet, not so much -§who's a clever boy-¨ as -§who's a funny boy-¨! Flying fails, performing Parrots and the real life angry birds -V we've assembled the very best the web has to offer, guaranteed to make you laugh out loud.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Because of her love for cats, Claire carefully created a place called "There is a Cat at the Corner". While enjoying your meals and drinks, more than a dozen beautiful cats are strolling freely in the store, waiting to interact with you up close and enjoy a slow life with you. However, if you want to pet the cat yourself and win their favor, you must first understand the nature and preferences of cats! Claire also generously shares her "experiences in ruling over dozens of cats", which is extremely precious. Novice cat lovers should come and have a look!

programme.title: The Dog Rescuers
programme.desc: Baxter is a Shih-Tzu that was discovered abandoned in an empty house on the outskirts of Manchester; thin and with extremely matted fur. Inspector Lyndsey Taylor comes to the rescue, but until all that fur is removed, nobody knows what lies beneath.

programme.title: Zoo Vet At Large
programme.desc: Greyhound trainer John Thompson calls on Dr. Matt for help to get his lame star runner back on track. Matt removes a thorn from the greyhound's foot, but the pressure's on to get him fit enough for the next big race.

programme.title: Have A Pet Day
programme.desc: Renowned Golden Bell awarded host Sandy Wu takes her beloved dog Hershey on outings, inviting celebrities and their adorable pets to join in the fun. Beyond exploring nature, the show delves into heartfelt conversations about the journey of pet ownership and shares touching stories amid delightful scenery and cuisine. The program features various enjoyable activities where owners and pets can bond, creating unforgettable memories through laughter and tears.

programme.title: Zoo Vet At Large
programme.desc: In this programme Dr. Matt saves the life of Iggy the Iguana -V by pulling his tail off!

programme.title: The Dog Rescuers
programme.desc: At an address in the Wirral, Inspector Anthony Joynes finds two collie crosses, Patch and Socks. Both dogs are in very poor condition and Anthony needs to get them out. Inspector Herchy Boal is called to Scooby's rescue. She's collapsed with puncture wounds after fighting with two other dogs. Scooby is in shock so she needs urgent medical care.

programme.title: Cute Pets At Home
programme.desc: Brother Hui, who runs an amphibian and reptile store in Xinxing District, Kaohsiung City, has a wide range of knowledge in the field of reptiles. He started with red-eared sliders and gradually got in touch with tortoises, lizards, snakes and other reptile pets. In Brother Hui's brick-and-mortar store, the most special existence is the two store pets, the South American lizards. The male is called Meatball and the female is called Porkball. How did their fate with Brother Hui begin? Brother Hui, who has many years of experience in raising South American lizards, also generously share his breeding secrets. How to distinguish male and female South American lizards? How to keep them healthy? What's the secret to taming them? In this epsiode, we unpack the living environment of South American lizards and reveal the breeding guide!

programme.title: ...Make You Laugh Out Loud
programme.desc: From Christmas as you've never experienced it before, with out-of-tune carol singers, Santa getting stuck, ungrateful children and exploding Christmas puddings - to OAP's, kids and even blundering burglars, six brand spanking new topics are given the trademark LOL treatment, combining user-generated footage with comic narration by comedian Iain Lee. programme.desc: Genus Pterophyllum, commonly known as P. scalare, freshwater angelfish or just angelfish is a large tropical fish native to the Amazon River in South America.They have a laterally flattened body, making them suitableto live in the crevices of tree roots in rivers with smooth water flow, and feeds on aquatic insects. The water temperature should be maintained at 26℃, and should reach 27-28℃ when breeding. The fertilized eggs are then released and attached to water plants or rocks, and the couple will take care of them together. However, once the eggs are hatched, the bigger ones will eat the smaller ones, hence not suitable to be raised together with other small fishes.

programme.title: Sasquatch Mountain Man - S01:E01 - British Colombia Moose
programme.desc: Conoce a Laramy Sasquatch Miller, uno de los últimos hombres de montaña de las Montañas Rocosas. Laramy Sasquatch Miller, de ascendencia india y entrenado por auténticos montañeses, sólo utiliza un arco hecho a mano y un rifle Hawken tradicional del calibre 54 para recorrer la ruta de los montañeses. Desde las profundidades de las Rocosas canadienses hasta las llanuras del Medio Oeste, cazando, cazando con trampas y sobreviviendo de la tierra.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E12 - Naturally Vibrant
programme.desc: El sur de Moravia, en la República Checa, alberga una gran variedad de hermosas orquídeas. Desde allí nos dirigimos al Caribe, a Cuba, con sus vistas de increíble belleza contrastadas con brutales peleas de gallos. De Cuba viajamos a Fiyi, en el Océano Pacífico, a menudo considerado un verdadero paraíso en la Tierra.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E13 - Naturally Hewn
programme.desc: En este episodio viajamos del Sur al Norte de Tierra Santa, Israel, deteniéndonos para admirar las vistas y empaparnos de la importancia bíblica de los lugares históricos. Continuamos hacia los Altos del Golán, en el Norte, donde el conflicto reciente sigue siendo muy evidente, y concluimos nuestra peregrinación en las orillas de Galilea.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S02:E01 - Naturally Wild
programme.desc: Muchas islas se encuentran en el mar entre Gran Bretaña y Escandinavia. Todas estas islas habrían permanecido cubiertas de nieve y la vida no habría sido sostenible de no ser por la Corriente del Golfo. Las aguas cálidas que fluyen por el Océano Atlántico hasta Sudamérica explican el clima templado de las islas, su rica naturaleza y una historia que se remonta miles de años atrás. Así son las tres islas que vamos a visitar hoy en Milagros de la Naturaleza: Vesterålen, la Isla Justa y las Orcadas.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S02:E02- Naturally Noble
programme.desc: Zimbabue era inicialmente Rodesia del Sur y se encuentra al sur de las cataratas Victoria, junto al río Zambeze. Zambia era inicialmente Rodesia del Norte y se encuentra en la otra orilla del río. Zimbabue es un país sin salida al mar situado en el sureste de África. Limita al sur con Sudáfrica. Según los arqueólogos, los primeros registros indican que los primeros asentamientos humanos en esta zona se remontan al siglo III.

programme.title: Jim Shockey's Uncharted - S01:E06 - Heaven's Gate
programme.desc: Kyrgyzstan. Jim and Corey journey to the Tian Shan mountain range in search of high altitude mountain dwelling sheep and ibex.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E05 - The Clewiston Terror
programme.desc: Un enorme jabalí está aterrorizando a los trabajadores de una granja en Clewiston, Florida. Manny es llamado para llevar al cerdo ante la justicia.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E06 - Wild Boar Naples
programme.desc: Manny caza jabalíes con su lanza tridente.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E07 - Slaying the Port Labelle Monster
programme.desc: Manny se enreda con un cerdo monstruoso en los densos bosques de Port Labelle.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E08 - Save a Watermelon Kill a Boar Part 1
programme.desc: Manny sigue la pista de un jabalí que asalta campos de sandías en el suroeste de Florida.

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E11 - Most Poisonous
programme.desc: You wouldn’t want to be bitten by any of these but which one has the deadliest poison? The venom from the most poisonous snake on the planet? A rare poisonous lizard? Or is it the blue ringed octopus?

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E12 - Migration
programme.desc: Los animales, grandes y no tan grandes, recorren cientos de kilómetros, algunos en busca de comida, otros para encontrar el lugar ideal para reproducirse. Desde las cebras que atraviesan las sabanas africanas hasta los enormes viajes que emprenden las tortugas para encontrar la playa perfecta donde desovar, los viajes anuales, a menudo peligrosos, son simplemente alucinantes.

programme.title: Wild Ones - S01:E13 - Who is the King?
programme.desc: Se calcula que hay aproximadamente 8,7 millones de especies diferentes de animales en la Tierra. Cada una de ellas ha desarrollado técnicas y habilidades de supervivencia únicas, específicas y a menudo mortales. ¿Cómo elegir un favorito entre un abanico tan amplio de criaturas espectaculares y hermosas?

programme.title: Royal Documentaries - S01:E43 - Diana A Day In The Life
programme.desc: 當戴安娜訂婚時，她始終處於媒體的視野中。她在一生中專注於自己的兒子，並致力於慈善工作，例如對地雷發表意見。戴安娜利用自己的名氣來引起人們對這些和其他重要問題的關注。這部經過深思熟慮的節目更深入地研究了20世紀最驚人的人物之一。通過前所未見的畫面，它展示了她從一個害羞的少女走到成為威爾士公主戴安娜的歷程，包括她最後日子的感人時刻。

programme.title: Carter's W.A.R. - S02:E02 - The Heart of the Conflict
programme.desc: Investigando una serie de leones asesinados, Ivan llega al corazón mismo de un antiguo conflicto entre humanos y leones. El resultado pondrá a prueba los propios valores fundamentales de Ivan sobre la cultura

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E05 - Hanging by a Thread
programme.desc: Los pilotos de Tanalian Aviation Joel y Josiah se ganan la vida transportando una máquina de nieve varada.

programme.title: Alaska's Ultimate Bush Pilots - S02:E06 - Into The Deep
programme.desc: Los pilotos de bush tienen que utilizar todas sus habilidades -buceo, aparejo submarino y vuelo experto- para intentar salvar un ala de de Havilland Beaver en el fondo del lago 6 Mile.

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E07 - Operation Spotted Dog
programme.desc: Working to protect our treasured natural resources in some of the country's most secluded spots means there's never a boring day on the job.

programme.title: Wardens - S01:E08 - Operation Boat Float
programme.desc: In the shade of the wild mountains, the Yellowstone River transforms into a colorful spectacle during the yearly boat float weekend. Armed with jet boats, the Wardens gear up for a wild time, looking out for the river and helping out the wacky rafters.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E07 - The Journal
programme.desc: El pastor Mike Turner está haciendo una excursión en solitario a través de la divisoria continental en la implacable cordillera Wind Rivers de Wyoming cuando queda irremediablemente atrapado bajo una roca. En su diario relata su agotadora lucha de 11 días por sobrevivir.

programme.title: Fight to Survive - S02:E08 - Tree Stand Fall
